{"tid":1624780,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［宣言］公開認衰？冷處理？","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:09:50.000Z","uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cad96eaaf9c4ee2d7401852c7198e30ec2af1b5b","tid":1624780,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:50:14.000Z","msg":"宣言明顯令國際線動搖左。<br />\n唔割蓆，但手足的確走太前，民心未跟上。<br />\n<br />\n-襯而家仲係救火時間，<br />\n向國際認衰，同時指出政府步向極權，<br />\n香港已經有少數人想獨立，我地沒大台，<br />\n阻止唔到佢地發獨立宣言。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得效果比較好，不竟西方對年輕人有容錯態度<br />\n<br />\n-冷處理<br />\n咁多條戰線，衰一兩條係必然，其他國家都會冷處理<br />\n主要係驚對家煲大，作為外交遊說手段。<br />\n這次無疑送左子彈給人。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔好睇少依個失策，要盡早斷尾。"},{"pid":"149c76b7473ca17966dc41bd19fc000dafc32814","tid":1624780,"uid":270956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"冷處理得啦，Solomon都有幫手話係spy，雖然證實唔到"},{"pid":"193bd503b08c3d36c4ccc2887eae47d534185663","tid":1624780,"uid":260588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"冷處理喇<br />\n而家都仲可以話係共匪派奸細搞出嚟<br />\n不要越描越黑"},{"pid":"b809a0af3adec6a1d4b949f43cc8e725d9ee0256","tid":1624780,"uid":260588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149c76b7473ca17966dc41bd19fc000dafc32814","tid":1624780,"uid":270956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:51:48.000Z","msg":"冷處理得啦，Solomon都有幫手話係spy，雖然證實唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"佢都盡力為大家兜"},{"pid":"5bbb2354eba5add7db449184c39bcd8baa7b483f","tid":1624780,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:04:57.000Z","msg":"破壞得太過火可唔可以道歉?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太嬲先搞到咁<br />\n記得當無讀過宣言啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eac65172e6b83478b943ce053c9ad1c07de1826","tid":1624780,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"冷處理<br />\n你越講越多人坳"},{"pid":"6